name: Warmup_Div03_Sub01
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD3S1.CPF,
GmailD3S1.NOME,
GmailD3S1.EMAIL,
GmailD3S1.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD3S1.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD3S1.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD3S1.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD3S1.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV03_SUB01 GmailD3S1
UNION
